    "Lens modelling requires some form of the mass profile to be chosen first, e.g.",
    "SIE, power-law, etc, and proceeds by making specific assumptions for the (unknown) extended source brightness profile, including the quasar point source, and solving the lens equation to fit the lensed light components to the data (see Shajib et al. 2024).",
